---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Why Choose a Local Security Consultant? | Sheepdog Cyber Defense" description="Working with a local penetration testing company in Bulverte, Spring Branch, or San Antonio offers real advantages. Learn why local matters for your business security." showMatrix={true}>
  <section>
    <h1>Why Choose a Local Security Consultant?</h1>
    <p class="lead">When it comes to protecting your business, does it matter whether your security consultant is based in San Antonio or somewhere halfway across the country? Absolutely.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>You Get Face-to-Face Communication</h2>
    <p>Security isn't something you want to discuss through email tickets or across time zones. When you work with Sheepdog Cyber Defense, you're working with a local team that can jump on a call or meet in person when needed. Need to walk through a finding together? Want to discuss your security posture face-to-face? That's what we do.</p>
    <p>Local consultants understand the regional business landscape and can tailor recommendations accordingly.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Faster Response Times</h2>
    <p>When you discover a critical vulnerability or need urgent consultation, timezone differences matter. Working with a consultant in the Central Time Zone means:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Same-day response during business hours</li>
      <li>No waiting until tomorrow (or Monday) for urgent issues</li>
      <li>Ability to schedule on-site assessments quickly</li>
      <li>Real-time debriefs after testing completes</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Supporting Local Business</h2>
    <p>When you hire Sheepdog Cyber Defense, you're supporting a veteran-owned small business rooted in the Bulverde, Spring Branch, and San Antonio community. We live here, we work here, and we're invested in the success of local businesses.</p>
    <p>Your money stays in the local economy, and you build relationships that go beyond a transactional vendor relationship.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Understanding Regional Threats</h2>
    <p>Cyber threats aren't uniform across geography. Local consultants understand the specific risks facing Texas businesses—whether it's the particular industries prominent in the area, regional compliance requirements, or patterns seen in nearby companies.</p>
    <p>We know the local business community, which means we can provide contextually relevant security advice.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Accountability You Can Count On</h2>
    <p>Large national firms can treat you as just another account number. As a local consultant, our reputation is built on serving this community. We're here for the long haul, and our success depends on delivering results that keep our neighbors secure.</p>
    <p>When you call, you reach people who know your name and your business.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="cta">
    <h2>Work with a Local Team You Can Trust</h2>
    <p>Sheepdog Cyber Defense is proud to serve businesses in Bulverde, Spring Branch, San Antonio, and across South Central Texas. Let's discuss how we can help protect your business.</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn">Get in Touch</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .lead { font-size: 1.25rem; max-width: 700px; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  section { margin-bottom: 3rem; }
  ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; }
  li { color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  strong { color: var(--text); }
  .cta { padding-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); text-align: center; }
  .cta p { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
</style>
